      "side": 1,
      "message": "Cannot drop it, the two-parameter signature is required to match ExtensionLogAssociation type. Removing it would cause the function to register as DeleteFunction instead.\n\nHowever, I can drop the objectPath parameter from the inner function call in commit https://gerrit.openbmc.org/c/openbmc/phosphor-logging/+/88887 where it\u0027s passed as:\n```\nmanager-\u003elinkPELToEventLog(obmcId, objectPath);\n```\nSince it only takes obmcLogID, that second parameter can be removed from the call.",
